  "texts": [
    "• RQ4: Whether the proposed BiLLP framework is robust to different recommendation environments and base LLM models?",
    "Experiments SetupWe introduce the experimental settings with regard to simulated experiments and baselines, which are implemented based on the EasyRL4Rec libraryfoot_2 [56].",
    "Recommendation Experiments.In the interactive recommendation setting, we are interested in examining the potential of models to mitigate the issue of filter bubbles and maximize users' long-term engagement.",
    "Conducting direct online experiments for model learning and testing can be prohibitively costly.",
    "As a result, following [15], we resort to creating simulated interactive environments using high-quality logs.• Steam [25] contains reviews and game information."
  ]
